sentences: Birgitte Alsted   (born 15 June 1942) is a Danish violinist, teacher and composer.
Alsted was born in Odense, and was educated at the Royal Danish Academy of Music and in Warsaw.
Alsted has worked as a teacher in Hørsholm municipality in St. Annæ Gymnasium and in Copenhagen.
Nyvang and Alsted: Planetarium Music includes Sorgsang II (Lament II) (1995) by Alsted.
